  "title": "Warehouse Cleaner",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong> </p><ul><li>Sweep warehouse floors to maintain a clean and safe environment</li><li>Remove trash, recycling, and debris from all work areas</li><li>Clean and sanitize restrooms and offices within the warehouse</li><li>Clean spills promptly to prevent slips and other hazards</li><li>Use cleaning chemicals and equipment safely and correctly</li><li>Follow all health, safety, and sanitation guidelines</li><li>Report safety concerns or maintenance issues to supervisors</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to perform physical tasks such as standing, walking, bending, and lifting</li><li>Ability to follow instructions and safety procedures</li><li>Ability to work independently or as part of a team</li><li>Working Hours: Monday to Friday: 8am to 12noon</li></ul>",
